Barrymore, periksa interior.

867
01:19:26,803 --> 01:19:28,012
Dia pasti ada di sana.

868
01:19:28,179 --> 01:19:29,555
Barrymore?

869
01:19:29,722 --> 01:19:31,891
Siapa yang mengawasi kampus?

870
01:19:31,975 --> 01:19:34,018
